A table for the Uncomplicated Cesarean Rates. Data processed in 02-analyze-cesarean.

> Note that some of the same hospitals are listed under different names.

```{r setup, echo=F, results='hide', message=F, warning=F}
library(tidyverse)
library(DT)
```


```{r import, echo=F}
crate_all <- read_rds("data-processed/crate_all.rds") %>% 
  rename(
    NOTCESAREAN = N,
    CESAREAN = Y)
```


```{r table, echo=F}
crate_all %>% datatable()
```
